<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        @page { margin: 0; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #1f1147;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            padding: 60px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border: 20px solid #7c3aed;
            position: relative;
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        .border-inner {
            border: 2px solid #ddd6fe;
            height: 100%;
            padding: 40px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            position: relative;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #7c3aed;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 54px;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #1e1b4b;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #6d28d9;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .recipient-label {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .recipient-name {
            font-size: 38px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #1e1b4b;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            display: inline-block;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            min-width: 400px;
        }
        .description {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            color: #475569;
        }
        .formation-name {
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #7c3aed;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 60px;
            display: table;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .footer-cell {
            display: table-cell;
            width: 33%;
            vertical-align: bottom;
        }
        .signature-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #94a3b8;
            margin: 0 20px 10px 20px;
        }
        .footer-label {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
        }
        .stamp {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 40px;
            right: 40px;
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border: 4px double #7c3aed;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #7c3aed;
            font-weight: 900;
            transform: rotate(-15deg);
            opacity: 0.2;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="border-inner">
            <div class="logo">FINORA EDUCATION</div>
            
            <div class="title">MASTER CERTIFICATE</div>
            <div class="subtitle">DE RÉUSSITE ET D'EXCELLENCE</div>
            
            <div class="recipient-label">CE CERTIFICAT EST DÉCERNÉ À</div>
            <div class="recipient-name">{{ user.username|upper }}</div>
            
            <div class="description">
                Pour avoir complété avec succès l'intégralité du parcours de formation 
                <br>
                <span class="formation-name">"{{ formation.titre }}"</span>
                <br>
                comprenant l'ensemble des <strong>{{ totalLessons }} leçons</strong> et ayant validé 
                tous les examens de compétence correspondants.
            </div>
            
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #94a3b8;">Délivré le {{ date|date('d/m/Y') }} par la plateforme FINORA</p>

            <div class="footer">
                <div class="footer-cell">
                    <div class="signature-line"></div>
                    <div class="footer-label">DIRECTION PÉDAGOGIQUE</div>
                </div>
                <div class="footer-cell">
                    <!-- Space for dynamic logo or seal -->
                </div>
                <div class="footer-cell">
                    <div class="signature-line"></div>
                    <div class="footer-label">SECRÉTARIAT GÉNÉRAL</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="stamp">
                FINORA VALIDATED<br>OFFICIAL SEAL
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
